{"tid":1231249,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"知道金鐘烈士真正身份未","createTime":"2019-06-16T12:17:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T14:15:45.000Z","uid":103315,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"624124b284e9589833b43833834e599f07b9c347","tid":1231249,"uid":103315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T12:17:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />比料寫下墓誌銘都好呀"},{"pid":"1d9f0b662dce2b5109f31887a573de34f60f11dc","tid":1231249,"uid":202912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T12:20:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cca59972ccef1ebec8741da8fa409cab794b2edc","tid":1231249,"uid":103315,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T13:31:43.000Z","msg":"剛剛得悉，昨日殉國殉港的烈士，是與我們一起佔旺戰友。<br />\n本人謹代表熱血公民全體向烈士的家人及朋友致以最深切的慰問。願他在天有靈繼續保佑一眾義士及行動者，願安息。<br />\n<br />\n另外，今日有一位善心人聯絡我們，她是從事殯儀工作的朋友，希望可以能為梁先生義舉一場法事，讓他能夠體面地離開。<br />\n<br />\n最後，希望大家平安。<br />\n<br />\n熱血公民主席<br />\n立法會議員鄭松泰<br />\n<br />\n2019年6月16日"},{"pid":"9fc1de0e57a6d231b750cf4eb378a9c08f58a905","tid":1231249,"uid":103315,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T13:57:55.000Z","msg":"昨晚於金鐘太古廣場墮斃的男子梁凌杰(35歲)，曾於2014年佔中時期走到旺角街頭抗爭。據悉，梁曾任職地盤散工，現時無業，家中父母及姐姐。於佔旺時認識梁凌杰的黃先生透露，梁外號「化骨龍」，為人沉默，性格較衝動，多次與警員爆發衝突，黃曾提醒對方「唔好太激」。據黃先生了解，梁凌杰尋死原因，是對特區政府心灰意冷「103萬人嘅意見都冇人理。」<br />\n<br />\n黃先生形容，梁凌杰有犧牲精神，不介意犧牲自己以喚醒旁人，當年佔旺時，警方採取拘捕行動，梁亦身先士卒。雖然雙方於佔旺結束後並無聯絡，黃先生得悉梁凌杰墮樓仍深感悲痛。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190616/59723149\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190616%2F59723149&d=q0LkGBAelTJmoxhYCIypyUHQxt1T4ELL4DwIHxiqIsg%3D&h=97a1c05f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190616%2F59723149&h=ce6aacba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190616/59723149</a>"},{"pid":"44474461d140fe0e602145d773e72788e9cd1a08","tid":1231249,"uid":259530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:15:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}